    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="item active">
        <img src="/assets/slider/first_slider.png" alt=""/>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <p>网络时代，变革大学教育的践行者。</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-large btn-primary" href="sign_up.html">注册</a></p>
